---
// Products component - Product Catalog
---

<section id="products" class="py-10 bg-slate-50" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:products">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8c">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8d">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-[#E85D1A] uppercase mb-3 block" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8e">Product Catalog</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-950 tracking-tighter mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8f">Our Core Power Solutions.</h3>
      <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8f-desc">
        From standard distribution units to fully custom-engineered special type transformers — every Elsan product is manufactured to IEC 60076 and tested to international standards before dispatch.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8g">
      <!-- Product 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:border-[#E85D1A] transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:product-1">
        <div class="text-[#E85D1A] mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8h">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8i">Distribution Transformers</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8j">Pole-mounted and pad-mounted units designed for efficient, reliable power delivery across urban, rural, and industrial electricity networks with minimal energy loss.

→Rated capacity: 25 kVA to 2,500 kVA
→Low- and medium-voltage configurations available
→High-permeability core for minimal energy loss
→Oil-immersed and dry-type options
→Compliant with IEC and Nigerian grid standards
→Custom voltage ratios and tap configurations on request


Widely supplied to DISCOs, state electricity boards, and industrial operators across Nigeria and West →Africa.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:azh723">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#E85D1A]" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8k">25kVA - 2500kVA</span>
          <a href="/distribution-transformers/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-[#E85D1A] text-[#E85D1A] font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#E85D1A] hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:euisp">
            Detailed Information
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:border-[#E85D1A] transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:product-2">
        <div class="text-[#E85D1A] mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8l">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8m">Power Transformers</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8n">Heavy-duty, high-capacity units built for substation, transmission, and large industrial applications — engineered to handle demanding load profiles with high efficiency and operational stability.

 → Rated capacity: 3.15 MVA to 50 MVA
 → Suitable for substation, grid, and heavy industrial use
 → Advanced insulation and cooling systems (ONAN / ONAF)
 → On-load and off-load tap changer options
 → Full factory routine testing to IEC 60076
 → Custom engineering for non-standard specifications.



 Ideal for transmission substations, independent power producers (IPPs), and large industrial facilities operating on the Nigerian national grid.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:azh724">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#E85D1A]" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8o">3.15MVA - 50MVA</span>
          <a href="/power-transformers/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-[#E85D1A] text-[#E85D1A] font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#E85D1A] hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:euiso">
            Detailed Information
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:border-[#E85D1A] transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:product-3">
        <div class="text-[#E85D1A] mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8p">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8q">Single Phase Units</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8r">Elsan's single phase distribution transformers are designed for pole-mounted installations serving specific utility, rural electrification, and catenary system applications across Nigeria.

 →Rated capacity: up to 160 kVA
 →Pole-mounted configuration
 →Suitable for utility and catenary systems
 →Oil-immersed construction for outdoor durability
 →Compliant with IEC and Nigerian grid standards
 →Custom voltage ratios available on request.




Particularly suited to rural electrification programmes and last-mile electricity access projects across Nigeria and neighbouring West African countries.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:azh725">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#E85D1A]" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8s">Up to 160kVA</span>
          <a href="/single-phase-units/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-[#E85D1A] text-[#E85D1A] font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#E85D1A] hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:euisn">
            Detailed Information
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:border-[#E85D1A] transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:product-4">
        <div class="text-[#E85D1A] mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-left" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8t">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8u">Special Type Transformers</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8v">Custom-engineered solutions designed for applications that fall outside standard configurations — from dual voltage capability to solar and photovoltaic systems.

 →Dual voltage capability configurations
 →Solar and photovoltaic (PV) plant applications
 →Renewable energy and off-grid system integration
 →Tailored winding configurations and voltage ratios
 →Custom cooling class and insulation level on request
 →Full engineering consultation and factory testing included




Increasingly specified for Nigeria's growing solar and off-grid renewable energy sector, as well as specialist industrial applications across West Africa.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:azh726">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#E85D1A]" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:p4vf8w">Custom Engineering</span>
          <a href="/special-type-of-transformers/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-[#E85D1A] text-[#E85D1A] font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#E85D1A] hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" data-ps="src/components/home/Products.astro:euism">
            Detailed Information
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
